OL,3,CFormer Tory MP Lee Anderson joins
OL,4,CReform UK
OL,6,FThe MP for Ashfield was suspended last
OL,7,Fmonth over claims 'Islamists' had 'got
OL,8,Fcontrol' of London Mayor Sadiq Khan,
OL,9,FITV News Political Correspondent Harry
OL,10,FHorton reports
OL,12,FFormer Tory MP Lee Anderson has
OL,13,Fdefected to Reform UK, saying he could
OL,14,Fnot be a member of a party that
OL,15,F"stifles free speech".
OL,17,FThe move, which comes after weeks of
OL,18,Fspeculation about a possible defection
OL,19,Fby Mr Anderson, gives Reform UK its
OL,20,Ffirst MP.
