OL,6,FThe Ashfield MP told ITV News last
OL,7,Fmonth he would never apologise for
OL,8,Fwhat he said, even if it meant he had
OL,9,Fto "stand down or not stand at all".
OL,11,FWhen asked about whether he would join
OL,12,FReform UK, he said "I'm not prepared
OL,13,Fto discuss my political journey beyond
OL,14,Fthis week."
OL,16,FMr Anderson will now have represented
OL,17,Fthree different parties after
OL,18,Fpreviously being a member of the
OL,19,FLabour party - being elected as a
OL,20,FLabour councillor in the 2015 Ashfield
OL,21,FDistrict Council elections.
